1. What is EXTRACT in SQL?
   EXTRACT is used to get specific parts of a date/time value
   Like extracting year, month, day, hour, etc.
   Helps in filtering and grouping data based on date
   Mostly used in reporting and analytics queries

Syntax
EXTRACT(field FROM date_column)

2. Common Fields Used
YEAR
MONTH
DAY
HOUR
MINUTE
SECOND

